<font size="15" name="Arial" color="#7CB500">Because Life is not only </font><font size="20" name="Arial" color="#24211D">B</font><font size="20" name="Arial" color="#FFFFFF">L</font><font size="20" name="Arial" color="#24211D">A</font><font size="20" name="Arial" color="#FFFFFF">C</font><font size="20" name="Arial" color="#24211D">K</font><font size="15" name="Arial" color="#7CB500"> and </font><font size="20" name="Arial" color="#FFFFFF">W</font><font size="20" name="Arial" color="#24211D">H</font><font size="20" name="Arial" color="#FFFFFF">I</font><font size="20" name="Arial" color="#24211D">T</font><font size="20" name="Arial" color="#FFFFFF">E</font>

638
01:25:04,082 --> 01:25:06,915
You and the others better lay low
for a few days.

639
01:25:08,219 --> 01:25:11,814
I'll keep this. You go.
Wallace will let you know.

640
01:25:24,235 --> 01:25:26,703
- Bring me Carson.
- Right.

641
01:25:41,252 --> 01:25:44,244
Angel Eyes said for us
to lay low for a few days.

642
01:25:44,556 --> 01:25:47,582
But we'll keep close enough
to keep an eye on things.

643
01:25:47,992 --> 01:25:49,926
Come on, saddle your horses.

644
01:26:00,672 --> 01:26:02,037
Come on in, Tuco.

645
01:26:02,807 --> 01:26:04,297
Don't be bashful.

646
01:26:05,210 --> 01:26:07,474
There's no formalities, here.

647
01:26:18,790 --> 01:26:20,758
It's been a long time!

648
01:26:24,395 --> 01:26:25,589
You're hungry.

649
01:26:26,598 --> 01:26:28,259
Sit down. Eat!

650
01:26:47,719 --> 01:26:49,482
I knew it, I knew it!

651
01:26:51,322 --> 01:26:53,483
The minute I saw you, I said to myself:

652
01:26:54,626 --> 01:26:57,026
"Look at that pig, Angel Eyes...

653
01:26:58,463 --> 01:27:00,897
"...I'll bet he's got himself an easy job!

654
01:27:04,269 --> 01:27:06,260
"And he never forgets a friend!"

655
01:27:07,138 --> 01:27:09,265
I never forget old friends, Tuco.

656
01:27:13,244 --> 01:27:15,212
It's good to see old friends again.

657
01:27:18,483 --> 01:27:21,145
Especially when they come
from so far away...

658
01:27:21,920 --> 01:27:24,184
...and have so much to talk about.
